Why Educated People Fall for Digital Arrest Scams
Fake Loan Apps: The Silent Mental Health Crisis
Introduction

In recent years, cybercrime in India has evolved far beyond poorly written phishing emails. One of the most alarming trends is the rise of Digital Arrest Scams and Fake Loan Apps, where even highly educated professionals—engineers, teachers, IT employees—are falling victim.

