What Is a Digital Arrest Scam?

A Digital Arrest Scam is a social-engineering attack where scammers impersonate:

Police officers

CBI / ED officials

Telecom regulators

Victims are told:

Their Aadhaar or phone number is linked to illegal activity

An “online arrest” is underway

They must stay on video call and transfer money to “verify innocence”

These scams rely not on technical hacking, but on fear, authority, and urgency.

Why Educated People Become Easy Targets

Contrary to popular belief, education does not equal cyber awareness.

Key reasons include:

Authority Bias
Educated individuals often trust institutions and official language.

Overconfidence
Many believe scams only target the “uneducated,” lowering their guard.

Professional Pressure
Fear of reputation damage pushes victims to act quickly.

Sophisticated Scripts
Scammers use legal terms, case IDs, and fake documents.

According to Codevirus Security Pvt. Ltd., attackers carefully study human psychology more than technology.

Fake Loan Apps: A Growing Mental Health Emergency

Fake loan apps pretend to offer:

Instant loans

Zero documentation

Low interest rates

Once installed, these apps:

Steal contacts, photos, and messages

Harass victims using threats and humiliation

Pressure users into paying inflated “penalties”

Mental Health Impact

Victims experience:

Anxiety and depression

Sleep disorders

Social isolation

In extreme cases, self-harm

This makes fake loan apps not just a financial crime, but a mental health crisis.

Cyber awareness initiatives by Codevirus Security Pvt. Ltd.
 emphasize that prevention starts with education, not fear.

How to Protect Yourself

No law enforcement conducts arrests over video calls

Do not install apps outside Play Store/App Store

Never share OTPs, Aadhaar, or PAN details

Report scams immediately to cybercrime.gov.in

Conclusion

Cybercrime today targets the mind, not machines. Educated users must upgrade their awareness to match evolving scam tactics. Organizations like Codevirus Security Pvt. Ltd., a Top 10 Cyber Security Services Company in Lucknow, play a crucial role in spreading cyber literacy and protecting digital citizens.
